data.description: Prepare to be dazzled by this stunning residence! If you're in search of an exceptional family home, look no further – this gem has it all! Nestled gracefully alongside the 9th hole of the prestigious guard-gated River Hills Golf Community, this double lot home is sure to have you packing your bags! This home has been impeccably maintained by its current owner, & it shows! Some of the big-ticket upgrades include a full kitchen remodel 2018, NEW ROOF 2017, A/C ducts and handlers 2018, NEW water heater in 2022, UV hurricane film on all windows and sliders 2018, hurricane garage doors 2023, custom California closets in all bedrooms & so much more! OH, and did we mention over 50k worth of hurricane-grade steel screen roll-downs and mesh that covers all exterior windows and doors, providing an extra level of safety for your family! Picture yourself stepping through the front door to be greeted by the breathtaking view of the glistening pool and the lush green fairways beyond. Instantly setting the stage for entertaining, the formal living and dining areas offer an inviting ambiance for cherished moments with family and friends. For culinary enthusiasts, the gourmet kitchen is a work of art, featuring top-of-the-line appliances including an induction range top with double ovens and a subzero refrigerator, stunning quartz counters with granite sink, custom cabinetry, and a welcoming center island that beckons guests to gather around. Adjacent to this culinary haven, the family room was thoughtfully designed for both relaxation and entertainment. Cozy up by the beautiful gas fireplace on tranquil evenings while taking in the panoramic golf course views. Escape to your own personal retreat – the primary suite is a private wing of luxury and comfort. Unwind in the spacious sitting area, enjoying the serene views of the lanai. The en-suite bath is a spa-like haven, featuring an oversized jetted tub, a generous walk-in shower, double vanities, and exquisite granite countertops. Additional spacious bedrooms, strategically situated in a separate wing of the home, offer large closet space and share a well-appointed bath. Meanwhile, a versatile fourth bedroom at the front of the house offers endless possibilities – use it as a private office, a playroom, a nursery, or a game room, catering to your unique lifestyle needs. But wait, it gets even better! Step outside to discover an incredible outdoor oasis that will leave you in awe. A vast covered lanai with a screened-in, gas-heated, and sparkling pool and spa awaits. For added privacy, a roll-down sun shed completes the picture. And if you seek more space for recreation, the backyard delivers in abundance. In addition to the world-class golf course, residents can enjoy miles of picturesque walking trails, a clubhouse with a fitness center and restaurant, tennis courts, and a lap pool. And let's not forget about the convenience of being located within the sought-after zone of A-rated schools. View this home virtually with this link: my.matterport.com/show/?m=LZJ594Bq7Mc&mls=1
